## Limitations

The findings are based on available data and projections, which may change as new research emerges. The complexity of climate change and its multifaceted impacts on health make it challenging to predict specific outcomes accurately. Additionally, the focus on certain regions or populations may not fully represent global variations in climate change effects. Further research is needed to explore the long-term health impacts and effective mitigation strategies.